Interface FormatHintInput

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractDateInput, AppUserFactory.AppUserNameInput, DateInput, DurationInput, ElapsedSecondInput, EmailInput, EmailListInput, MonthInput, RangeDateInput, RelativeDateInput, TimeStampInput

    public interface FormatHintInput
    Interface for Inputs that can provide a hint to the expected format of the required input. These can be implemented in the same way as TagInput or can be implemented as placeholder text.
